{"tid":351614,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)接左主人返屋企 但佢唔肯食嘢","createTime":"2017-08-08T07:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T04:52:39.000Z","uid":19460,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb4312a326cee79e1d065fd5a010d7f1f0f9084","tid":351614,"uid":19460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:59:53.000Z","msg":"佢肯比我抱同摸 不過一落地就里埋<br />\n<br />\n黎左兩個鐘都唔肯食嘢<br />\n<br />\n小弟新手貓奴 主人3個月大 舊主人冇帶過佢去打針<br />\n想問我應該幾時帶主人去打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋點先可以領佢食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後奉上主人寫真一張<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/155938_f3695b76f4d9d4f18089d75d28851b6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F155938_f3695b76f4d9d4f18089d75d28851b6b.jpg&h=15943078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29213aa52e668f2e181af360bc29e24f73182843","tid":351614,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"d糧濕少少水試下<br />\n針就已經要打 <br />\n俾少少時間佢認識下新環境"},{"pid":"937304eec24ec927fcca4390f5ac2a2aebf4bddf","tid":351614,"uid":123224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:06:57.000Z","msg":"慢慢嚟啦,比啲時間佢平靜下,將心比己你去到陌生地方都會驚啦"},{"pid":"9d1423caa51be43cf380603ace337233f2b29a3b","tid":351614,"uid":19460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567d4714d6f8656e34fb21aa9454eff7f348e99c","tid":351614,"uid":90266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"巴打你同我之前一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主子對陌生環境未慣姐 <br />\n我果時果隻黎左成日兜糧都無少過、佢又周圍收埋自己，但又俾抱，情況同你好近似。等佢自己熟悉下環境啦，好多時你地訓晒佢就自然會出黎食野去廁所。<br />\n記住廁所同野食、床要分得開啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038d0f5c06e3ccf1ecec6e647570e65d385ce178","tid":351614,"uid":90266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:24:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你同我之前一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主子對陌生環境未慣姐 <br />\n我果時果隻黎左成日兜糧都無少過、佢又周圍收埋自己，但又俾抱，情況同你好近似。<span style=\"color: red;\">放好野食、貓沙同床</span>係顯眼位置等佢自己熟悉下環境啦，好多時你地訓晒佢就自然會出黎食野去廁所。<br />\n記住廁所同野食、床要分得開啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"aaa4d6609c2035f86277cd41c160363ea6a64619","tid":351614,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:25:32.000Z","msg":"由得佢<br />\n定左會自己出黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe85cdb2b4033d217d83b670277d117ec4bfc87","tid":351614,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:45:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4d9f61d524034315730d1dbb18a0d3cc108120f","tid":351614,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"俾d時間同空間佢"},{"pid":"6aff0ae28234b565ec01825f8be3d42367db18ca","tid":351614,"uid":97708,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:06:00.000Z","msg":"你第一次上條女屋企咪又係成碌柒咁坐係到話伯母你好"},{"pid":"424cffb01a160085a6fb039202a6bfe3ecb9758a","tid":351614,"uid":122807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:43:54.000Z","msg":"你帶左佢返你屋企之後,起碼要俾佢住2星期先好帶佢去打針"},{"pid":"6bd6d6898997b0263eba909cf6ad3d18bb09dbfd","tid":351614,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:46:51.000Z","msg":"我隻貓細個嗰時嚟到都係喱埋起間我預備畀佢嘅屋仔入面<br />\n我無理過佢 等佢自己冷靜下<br />\n過咗幾個鐘出嚟就食咗啲嘢同埋玩 <br />\n再隔一陣就痾咗督尿<br />\n之後就生活愉快"},{"pid":"ef3f3c7dd322660fbab2bb9ebb6b83ba591f349d","tid":351614,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:50:13.000Z","msg":"我以前放左糧唔食<br />\n2個鐘後會收起<br />\n<br />\n最後隻貓第2日開始自己肚餓都係咁食"},{"pid":"6cc79e8607a0cdea936a8a242711a9b4a416b6c9","tid":351614,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}